parent1.code: A watercolor of three vibrant hummingbirds in the style of magical realism. They hover around a giant, bioluminescent flower in a misty rainforest at twilight, sipping nectar from its petals, with glowing fireflies and mysterious floating orbs illuminating the scene.

offspring.code: A mesmerizing watercolor of three iridescent hummingbirds in the style of surrealist magical realism. They gracefully hover around a colossal bioluminescent flower in a mystical rainforest at twilight, delicately sipping shimmering nectar from its translucent petals, with enchanted fireflies and prismatic orbs illuminating the dreamlike scene.
